con:config.con:query: select TRANSACTIONSID, PAYMENTTYPE, PAYMENTSTATUS, PRIORITIZED from TRANSACTIONS where TRANSACTIONSID = '${Properties#transactionId}'

select A.TRANSACTIONSID, A.PAYMENTTYPE, A.PAYMENTSTATUS, A.PRIORITIZED, A.RELEASEDATE, A.FK_PROCESSINGLINEID, A.CHARGEBEARER, A. BOOKINGLEVEL, C.INITIATORBANKID, C.MARKETTYPE, A.DEBIT_BOOKING_ID, D.* from TRANSACTIONS A, PAYMENTINFO B, MESSAGE C, RESERVATION_DETAILS D where A.TRANSACTIONSID = '${Properties#transactionId}' and A.FK_PAYMENTINFOID = B.PAYMENTINFOID and B.FK_MESSAGEID = C.MESSAGEID and A.TRANSACTIONSID = D.FK_TRANSACTIONSID order by RESERVATION_TYPE asc
